	* tests/runtime/System/TestArray.cs: add test for Array.Clear() called
	with empty array, index=0 and length=0.

2006-10-26  Heiko Weiss <heiko.weiss@de.trumpf-laser.com>

	* Xsharp/InputOutputWidget.cs: fixed problem with Expose and destroyed handle.

2006-10-21  Radek Polak <psonek2@seznam.cz>

	* System.Xml/XmlTextReader.cs: reset current node when end of document
	is reached. Without this Depth property was 1 even when whole document
	was read.

	* tests/System.Xml/TestXmlTextReader.cs: test for Depth property.

